---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>Clinic Flow Studio</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
      background: #f6f1e7;
      color: #2f3a2f;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dfe8d5, #f6f1e7);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background: #4f6b4f;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

/* 📱 MOBILE FIX */
@media (max-width: 768px) {

  body {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 32px !important;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 24px !important;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 16px !important;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .container {
    padding: 30px 16px !important;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 40px 16px !important;
  }

  /* Stack grids into single column */
  div[style*="grid-template-columns"] {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }

  /* Make cards breathe */
  .card {
    padding: 18px !important;
  }

}
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <Header />

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Clinic Flow Studio</h1>

    <p>
      Thoughtfully designed veterinary templates to simplify clinic life,
      reduce overwhelm, and help veterinary professionals stay organized.
    </p>

    <a class="button" href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/ClinicFlowStudioCo">
      Visit My Etsy Shop
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">

    <h2 style="text-align:center;">What You'll Find</h2>

    <div class="grid">

      <div class="card">
        📝 Printable Veterinary Forms
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        📊 Workflow & Organization Tools
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        📅 Clinic Tracking Systems
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">

    <h2>Created for Real Clinic Life</h2>

    <p style="max-width:700px; margin:auto;">
      Every template is designed with simplicity, efficiency,
      and real veterinary workflows in mind —
      helping busy clinics feel a little calmer and more organized.
    </p>

  </section>
<section class="section" style="text-align:center;">

<section class="section" style="text-align:center;">

  <h2>Featured Template ✨</h2>

  <p style="max-width:700px; margin:auto;">
    Designed for busy veterinary professionals who need clarity, structure, and simplicity in their daily workflow.
  </p>

  <div style="
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 40px auto 0;
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  ">

    <!-- PRODUCT IMAGE -->
    <img src="/public/patient-history-form.png"
         alt="Patient History Form Template"
         style="width:100%; border-radius:12px; margin-bottom:20px;" />

    <h3>Patient History Form Template</h3>

    <p>
      A clean, easy-to-use veterinary template designed to help clinics stay organized,
      reduce stress, and streamline patient documentation.
    </p>

    <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/ClinicFlowStudioCo"
       target="_blank"
       style="
         display:inline-block;
         margin-top:15px;
         background:#4f6b4f;
         color:white;
         padding:12px 22px;
         border-radius:999px;
         text-decoration:none;
         font-weight:600;
       ">
      View on Etsy
    </a>

  </div>

</section>

</section>

  <h2>Meet My Pets 🐾</h2>

  <p style="max-width:700px; margin:auto;">
    A big part of my inspiration comes from the animals I share my life with.
    They remind me daily why veterinary care, compassion, and organization matter so much.
  </p>

  <div style="
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap:20px;
    margin-top:40px;
  ">

   <div style="background:white; padding:28px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
    <h3>Juno</h3>

    <p>
      Juno is the self-appointed Head of Neighborhood Security and Chief Snack Quality Inspector.
      Equal parts athlete and cuddle consultant, Juno specializes in enthusiastic greetings,
      strategic squirrel surveillance, and maintaining excellent morale around the house.
    </p>

    <p>
      Known for a strong work ethic, dramatic zoomies,
      and a talent for locating the squeakiest toy in record time,
      Juno brings energy, loyalty, and just a little chaos to every team environment.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background:white; padding:28px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
    <h3>Luna</h3>

    <p>
      Luna is a charismatic people-person with extensive experience
      in comfort management and emotional support services.
    </p>

    <p>
      She excels in sunbeam supervision, treat negotiation,
      and making every visitor feel like the most important person in the world.
      With a calm but playful leadership style,
      Luna combines professionalism with an undeniable flair
      for stealing blankets and hearts alike.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background:white; padding:28px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
    <h3>Sushi</h3>

    <p>
      Sushi is an independent creative specialist
      with a background in advanced lounging techniques
      and late-night hallway athletics.
    </p>

    <p>
      Highly detail-oriented,
      Sushi maintains strict quality standards
      for nap locations and cardboard box inspections.
      While occasionally unavailable for meetings due to “personal reasons,”
      Sushi consistently delivers excellence in style,
      attitude, and mysterious stares from across the room.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background:white; padding:28px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
    <h3>Sriracha</h3>

    <p>
      Sriracha is a fast-moving operations expert
      best known for spicy personality traits
      and elite-level curiosity.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether conducting surprise countertop audits
      or sprinting through the house at 2 a.m.,
      Sriracha approaches every task with unmatched enthusiasm.
    </p>

    <p>
      A natural entertainer with strong communication skills
      (especially around mealtime),
      Sriracha keeps the household dynamic,
      efficient, and slightly on edge in the best possible way.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

</section>

  <Footer />

</body>
</html>
